articles.author: Jacopo Barigazzi
articles.title: Austria says Russia to cut off gas supplies on Saturday - POLITICO Europe
articles.description: Austrian Chancellor Karl Nehammer says there is a secure supply of alternative fuel and “no one will freeze this winter.”
articles.content:
It's unclear whether Russia has carried through with the threat, Euronews reported on Saturday. Gazprom is sending gas to Europe via Ukraine at normal levels, Bloomberg reported on Saturday.
